gov.nasa.jpl.mudrod.ontology

Interface Ontology

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    EsipCOROntology, EsipPortalOntology, LocalOntology

    public interface Ontology
    Base class for working with ontologies. Methods indicate ability to load, merge e.g. merge relevant ontology subgraphs into a new subgraph which can be used within Mudrod, subclass retreival, synonym expansion, etc.
    Author:
    lewismc
